{"tid":1604897,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得中共係用緊”君主論”治港？","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:54:19.000Z","uid":142763,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f12d55e3cb767fb13f6d3eb76fcd84988c12cfa7","tid":1604897,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"小弟睇緊嗰本係用英文寫，所以之後會有英文希望各位巴絲打唔好介意：<br />\n<br />\n係第5章:佔領前在自有法律之城市或君王國當如何統治。<br />\n<br />\n方法有三：<br />\n<br />\n第一種：徹底摧毀原有法律等舊制度<br />\n第二種：征服者坐鎮被征服地親自統治。<br />\n第三種：尊重原有法律等制度，但需要按期進貢，且建立一個忠心的「寡頭制」政府。<br />\n<br />\n而家仲係用緊第三種，但馬基維利認為第三種不可靠：「任何一個人要想成為一個自由城市的新生統治者，<span style=\"color: red;\">若不以摧毀這個城市作先決條件，那麼他所得到的報應則是坐以待斃。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n我覺中共而家做緊嘅嘢，同埋為咗統治香港佢哋會&rdquo;No surer way of keeping possession than by devastation&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\n如果習大帝同王滬寧係咁諗嘅話，香港可能之後會係一國一制。<br />\n<br />\n但之後會官逼民反，香港一定會獨立！"},{"pid":"25e180ed7fc7e24cdb9755e4d689702640785e93","tid":1604897,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f99f192d9c642f5f841f0ca8c628fc0c2e792cf6","tid":1604897,"uid":310266,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"讀cc讀到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e73a94059a4ff68349dbb1eb9b2a59af9f1a985","tid":1604897,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99f192d9c642f5f841f0ca8c628fc0c2e792cf6","tid":1604897,"uid":310266,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"讀cc讀到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"0cb55768afdd1aa917d200452d4439ea8b58bf8b","tid":1604897,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99f192d9c642f5f841f0ca8c628fc0c2e792cf6","tid":1604897,"uid":310266,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"讀